metadata.description:
This third-party compilation is one of three put together by an unknown person and spread on P2P networks, and acts as a 'best of' for Monotonik.

We decided it has excellent track choice (check out early tracks from Whiskas and Jiva in particular), plus a number of tracks only normally available in .MOD form as .MP3s, so we've made it an official release and added it to our catalog - the Internet and freely distributed music comes up with cool ideas like this if you're lucky.

Track listing (items with * have only previously been available in .MOD form):

1. JCole - "Lungs, Thank You"*
2. MD - "B"*
3. Super Science - "We're Like Air, Everywhere At Once"
4. Lindon - "Eksajoule"
5. XLLV - "Flying Mario (XLLV Remix)"
6. Serkul - "Boybie Socks"*
7. Thug - "Obatem By Night"
8. Prob - "Skyline"*
9. Sushi Brother - "Lionfish"
10. Whiskas - "As In Cockroach"*
11. Sleepy - "Foob"
12. Radix - "Counting Stars"
13. Lackluster - "13/10/99"
14. Sense - "Bubble Blower"
15. Jiva - "Unicorn"*
16. Jiva - "Desk"*
